channel.title: Hamachi account on other computer
channel.description:
Ive been using hamachi on a laptop all the time, but now I have my own computer back and i want to use the same username, my name on hamachi is habibi, so i logg in on hamachi with the name habibi and the same password. but now all the networks id join are away, it feels like ive just made a new account but with the same name. What can I do? I dont know all the servers in my head..
Well, to be honestly, I dont know any of em.
